aption-attachment-3518032" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3518032" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Grimes参加了在美国庆祝的2021 MET Gala" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Grimes@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518032" class="wp-caption-text"> Grimes参加了在美国庆祝的2021 Met Gala。图片来源：Theo Wargo/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>她继续强调，她打算在Coachella的第二个周末“亲自组织”她的文件，并补充说：“我不会再让这样的事情再次发生”，下周将是“完美无瑕的”。</p><p>在其他Coachella新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-cudi-joins-coachella-weekend-two-line-up-3618812">Kid Cudi已于周日（4月21日）从PDT下午5:10至PDT宣布在撒哈拉帐篷的特殊表演</a>。还值得注意的是，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">吸血鬼周末</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-join-coachella-2024-weekend-one-line-up-at-last-minute-3615769">今年Coachella开幕周末的惊喜</a>，他不会在周末表演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/coachella-2024-review-best-acts-3618348">阅读<em>NME</em>对Coachella 2024周末的整体评论</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/doja-cat-live-at-coachella-setlist-photos-3616933">Doja Cat的五星级标题表演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a>的突破以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/damon-albarn-tells-blurs-lackluster-coachella-crowd-youre-never-seeing-us-again-so-you-might-as-well-fucking-sing-it-3617844">不满的Damon Albarn</a> 。</p><p><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">在此处查看</a>有关Coachella 2024的最新新闻，评论以及更多信息。</em></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grimes-promises-to-cap-the-disarray-as-she-returns-for-coachella-weekend-two-3619916">格莱姆斯（Grimes）邮报（Post Grimes）承诺将“束缚混乱”，因为她回到Coachella Weekend Two，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
